==Description==

"The Heinrich Böll Foundation is a German, legally independent political foundation. Affiliated with the German Green Party,[1] it was originally founded in 1987 and rebuilt in 1997. The foundation was named after German writer Heinrich Böll (1917–1985)."
(http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heinrich_B%C3%B6ll_Foundation)

